 href="../files/2020/08/Development-Innovation-of-the-Lactation-Support-in-a-Telehealth-Setting-Course.docx">Summary Report</a> – Development &amp; Innovation of the Lactation Support in a Telehealth Setting Course</li>  <li><a href="../files/2020/08/Example-of-Unfolding-Case-Scenario-1-of-6.pdf">Example of Unfolding Case Scenario</a> (1 of 6)</li>  <li><a href="../files/2020/08/Case-1-Formative-Assessment-Rubric-from-SP.pdf">Case 1 Formative Assessment Rubric from SP</a></li>  <li><a href="../files/2020/08/Case-2-Formative-Assessment-Rubric-from-SP.pdf">Case 2 Formative Assessment Rubric from SP</a></li>  <li><a href="../files/2020/08/Case-3-Formative-Assessment-Rubric-from-SP.pdf">Case 3 Formative Assessment Rubric from SP</a></li>  <li><a href="../files/2020/08/Summative-Assessment-Rubric.pdf">Summative Assessment Rubric</a></li>  <li><a href="../files/2020/08/Encounter-Documentation-after-Telesimulation.pdf">Encounter Documentation after Telesimulation</a></li></ul><p><strong>Resultant Publications/Resources – </strong></p><ul>  <li><a href="https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/full/10.1177/2373379920977537?utm_term=2020-12-18&utm_campaign=sale_on_breastfeeding_simulators_and_highlights_from_2020&utm_medium=email&journalCode=phpa&utm_source=newsletter">Virtual Experiential Learning: A Description of an Internship Framework That Engages Students to Build Public Health Competencies</a></li>  <li><a href="https://www.liebertpub.com/doi/full/10.1089/bfm.2020.0253">The Efficacy of Hybrid Telesimulation with Standardized Patients in Teaching Medical Students Clinical Lactation Skills: A Pilot Study</a></li>  <li><a href="https://myumi.ch/2DqKe">Breastfeeding: Public Health Perspectives Massive Open Online Course (MOOC)</a></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p></div></div><?php include('../../../incl/footer.html'); ?>